📢 ANNOUNCEMENT

@US_EDA has awarded @LVGEA a $150,000 grant to support private capital investment and job creation in southern Nevada.

As southern Nevada continues to feel the impact of tariffs and plummeting tourism rates, this investment to create new jobs and diversify our economy is more important than ever.

Thank you to the Las Vegas Asian Chamber of Commerce for inviting me to their luncheon.

@LasVegas_ACC is a big reason why our AAPI businesses have such a strong and diverse economic footprint in Vegas.

Together, we can help businesses grow and create good jobs for our families.
